Package dbdrivers

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AdvancedQueries
    Runs advanced SQL queries on the OracleDB.
    CreateTables
    Creates all the tables required on OracleDB.
    Delete
    Deletes specific entries from a specified table given proper conditions.
    DropTables
    Drops all tables within the database
    OracleCon
    Connects to the OracleDB and provides disconnect functionality.
    PopulateTables
    Populates the tables of the database with pre-specified INSERT commands.
    Search
    Searches for a data entry in a table on the OracleDB given parameters to filter with.
    SimpleQueries
    Execute simple queries that are pre-specified
    Update
    Runs update queries on a desired table with desired updated information.
